HEADWORD: Fatalism
<hw>Fa"tal*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>fatalisme</ets>.]</ety> <def>The doctrine that all things are
subject to fate, or that they take place by inevitable
necessity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fatalist</ent>⟦br⟧
